⍝ EncloseAxis.tc
⍝ ══════════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: X simple scalar or vector nonneg int; X∊⍳⍴⍴B
      ⍝ inv: ⍴Z ←→ (⍴B)[(⍳⍴⍴B)∼X]   (axes not in X)
      B ← ⎕RVAL 3 (2 3 4) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      X ← 2                                  ⍝ enclose along axis 2
      Z ← ⊂[X]B
      (⍴Z) ≡ (⍴B)[(⍳⍴⍴B)∼X]
1
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ (⍴⍴B)-⍴,X
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ,(⍴⍴B)-⍴,X
1
      ⍝ inv: B ←→ ⊃[X]⊂[X]B
      B ≡ ⊃[X]⊂[X]B
1
      ⍝ inv: ⊂[⍳0]B ←→ ⊂¨B   (empty axis list)
      (⊂[⍳0]B) ≡ ⊂¨B
1
